'''Tetanne''' was a state on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Adumar/Legends|Adumar]]. Upon learning that renowned [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] [[General/Legends|General]] [[Wedge Antilles/Legends|Wedge Antilles]] would be leading the fight against [[Cartann]], they joined the coalition and fought in the [[Adumari Civil War]]. They eventually became part of the [[Adumari Union]].

